{"tid":1909833,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於中國科研團隊發現新冠病毒已突變","createTime":"2020-03-04T08:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T09:58:44.000Z","uid":38861,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d445d045d0c0dfad6ffcb989d5cf032c767138cd","tid":1909833,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"原文：<a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/nsr/advance-article/doi/10.1093/nsr/nwaa036/5775463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fnsr%2Fadvance-article%2Fdoi%2F10.1093%2Fnsr%2Fnwaa036%2F5775463&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=d82a60b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://academic.oup.com/nsr/advance-article/doi/10.1093/nsr/nwaa036/5775463</a><br />\n<br />\n整合：<br />\n有中國科學家嘗試依基因相似度及變異模式將武肺病毒分成為L及S型，並以兩者出現的頻率將病毒分成為較高侵略性及較低侵略性兩種。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n圖1為原文。﻿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EV8oMTm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEV8oMTm.jpg&h=e7d6ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n﻿<br />\n圖2為文中一細段文字，內容係講述雖然佢哋將病毒分成為L及S型，但某啲樣本係佢哋的界定下既不是S又不是L......﻿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c0gd862.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc0gd862.png&h=82c6b4b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n﻿<br />\n圖3為GISAID資料庫取圖，3月4日各病毒變異的大集合。藍色區域為變異地區，暫時尚未有與ACE2接合區域（RBD）的變異，並無科學理據可以指出佢哋所稱的S型、L型或非L非S的病毒任何一方較為有侵略性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6U5Kwkt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6U5Kwkt.jpg&h=8955fef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：武肺病毒一直在進行變異，但至今（3月4日）仍未有任何樣本發現武肺的ACE2 RBD出現任何變異，目前暫無明確理據病毒可以分出某一種病毒特別具侵略性與否。"},{"pid":"4b4301c96a62536c40499d411ab1a4d0e6bc0af4","tid":1909833,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cd0cb42a18347618a889c2df30d31717c1ab4d","tid":1909833,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"巴打高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd05fce9db1e2d96843ce0ab4a67c124cb1882e1","tid":1909833,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/Qn2XPG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FQn2XPG.gif&h=0a269be1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"696919cfa1cd3889d8b78c74d9d19c6a70a4ab1c","tid":1909833,"uid":103653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:00:45.000Z","msg":"Help Push sin"},{"pid":"18cc6557a97345de83d3907f7ad4d837606786fc","tid":1909833,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:01:58.000Z","msg":"變變變生命力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cd7527303f7c2f466b108b2cf025cb06c49a5a","tid":1909833,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"點變都唔緊要，最緊要死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4748890310b5e57ba627f0706c69849c0a646106","tid":1909833,"uid":50366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"繽紛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8170a480d1bde63001584dfc3d0e2726d2073b","tid":1909833,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57cd7527303f7c2f466b108b2cf025cb06c49a5a","tid":1909833,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"點變都唔緊要，最緊要死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"係黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"